TO: PASCAL COVICI

CC, 2 pp.





623 Highland Road

Ithaca, N.Y.

November 12, 1951

Dear Mr. Covici,

Many thanks for your charming letter. I shall be in New York on December 8, arriving late on Friday, the 7th, and leaving Sunday afternoon. I am delivering a lecture Saturday evening, but otherwise will be free 